
Ranger Help for: jungle
=======================

SUMMARY:    
The jungle terrain is almost a cross between forest and swamp. Its very
wooded, but also quite humid and moist. These two factors cause it to be
very foliated, with animals all about. The climate is usually hot and humid
with rain falling a lot of the time. The Ranger population is strong in
the jungle, since most of a Ranger's skills will work here. Kerei is
most noted for its jungles.

=============================================================================
